1044
00:43:12,576 --> 00:43:13,815
Hello!

1045
00:43:13,815 --> 00:43:17,755
I'm a Senior Intern Lee Man Sik, and I am joining your team today.

1046
00:43:17,815 --> 00:43:19,886
