00:43:20,185 --> 00:43:23,556
That kkondae boss is back.

1048
00:43:23,556 --> 00:43:25,426
What happened?

1049
00:43:26,255 --> 00:43:28,926
You can't just barge in like this.

1050
00:43:29,226 --> 00:43:31,465
The kkondae general manager is losing his place in the company.

1051
00:43:31,636 --> 00:43:34,766
