1054
00:43:38,875 --> 00:43:41,176
So, he ends up unemployed.

1055
00:43:41,476 --> 00:43:44,746
You think I'll have nowhere else to go?

1056
00:43:44,746 --> 00:43:48,016
That's right, he has nowhere else to go.

1057
00:43:49,915 --> 00:43:52,415
Meanwhile, there's a man...

1058
00:43:52,415 --> 00:43:54,355
