1060
00:43:57,926 --> 00:43:58,956
No way.

1061
00:43:58,956 --> 00:44:01,165
You need to bring me something!

1062
00:44:01,165 --> 00:44:04,235
Joon Soo is the Chairman's son, but losing his ground to Yeol Chan.

1063
00:44:04,235 --> 00:44:06,706
After hours of searching through...

1064
00:44:07,906 --> 00:44:10,935
This is it!

1065
00:44:10,976 --> 00:44:12,735
He scouted Man Sik as a senior intern,

1066
00:44:12,735 --> 00:44:15,076
knowing that Man Sik is Ga Yeol's weak point.

1067
00:44:15,446 --> 00:44:17,045
- Mr. Lee Man Sik. - Yes.

1068
00:44:17,045 --> 00:44:19,346
And so, they meet again,

1069
00:44:19,346 --> 00:44:21,985
but this time, the tables have turned.

1070
00:44:22,016 --> 00:44:23,585
Are you really okay with working for me?

1071
00:44:23,585 --> 00:44:25,855
What's wrong with that? I'm completely fine.

1072
00:44:25,855 --> 00:44:27,326
Then you better stick through.

1073
00:44:27,326 --> 00:44:28,326
Sure.

1074
00:44:28,355 --> 00:44:30,395
Where are your manners to your superior?

1075
00:44:30,895 --> 00:44:31,895
Yes, sir.

1076
00:44:31,895 --> 00:44:34,326
If you can't avoid it, you have to enjoy it.

1077
00:44:34,866 --> 00:44:38,196
Don't you expect elderly respect or kindness.

1078
00:44:39,536 --> 00:44:42,866
Yeol Chan decides to take his revenge on Man Sik.

1079
00:44:43,536 --> 00:44:46,206
Mr. Ga, would you like me to bring you a coffee?

1080
00:44:46,206 --> 00:44:49,676
I'd like espresso doppio lungo...

1081
00:44:49,676 --> 00:44:51,576
as a very dry cappuccino with whipped cream on top.

1082
00:44:51,576 --> 00:44:53,846
I'd also like chocolate drizzle and cinnamon powder on top.

1083
00:44:53,946 --> 00:44:54,946
Here's my card.

1084
00:44:55,415 --> 00:44:58,956
General Manager Ga is really taking his sweet revenge,

1085
00:44:58,956 --> 00:45:00,826
but this isn't the end.

1086
00:45:01,326 --> 00:45:04,926
This is impressive, I can tell that you've had...

1087
00:45:05,025 --> 00:45:06,866
30 years of experience in the field.

1088
00:45:07,065 --> 00:45:09,965
He acts so kind when there are people watching, but...

1089
00:45:10,536 --> 00:45:12,895
It's too old-fashioned, it's not worth reading.

1090
00:45:12,895 --> 00:45:15,165
He's savage when there are just the two of them.

1091
00:45:15,165 --> 00:45:17,335
Where is your proposal, Man Sik?

1092
00:45:17,335 --> 00:45:19,875
What? This dried pollack soup ramyeon is mine.

1093
00:45:20,005 --> 00:45:22,706
He also turns a blind eye on him when his idea gets stolen.

1094
00:45:22,875 --> 00:45:25,346
It's cold and raining, so what do you all say...

1095
00:45:25,346 --> 00:45:26,516
to some hot and spicy pizza?

1096
00:45:26,516 --> 00:45:29,386
I know that he can't eat a meal without soup.

1097
00:45:29,645 --> 00:45:31,056
Yeol Chan gave up...

1098
00:45:31,056 --> 00:45:33,215
on being the best boss ever to take his revenge.

1099
00:45:33,585 --> 00:45:37,625
It would have been great if his immature revenge worked.

1100
00:45:37,996 --> 00:45:40,395
Is that all you have? Copying me?

1101
00:45:40,395 --> 00:45:42,226
You're no match for me, punk.

1102
00:45:42,665 --> 00:45:45,735
He doesn't get affected by any criticism.

1103
00:45:46,636 --> 00:45:48,105
I need you to sway General Manager Ga.

1104
00:45:48,105 --> 00:45:50,306
What can I do?

1105
00:45:50,835 --> 00:45:52,906
With CEO Namgoong on his back,

1106
00:45:52,906 --> 00:45:55,875
he becomes even more thick-skinned.

1107
00:45:55,875 --> 00:45:58,215
No relationships are completely bad.

1108
00:45:58,215 --> 00:46:00,415
Smiling while reminiscing the past...

1109
00:46:00,415 --> 00:46:03,145
with whom I thought had an ill-fated relationship.

1110
00:46:03,145 --> 00:46:06,685
Rather, Yeol Chan was on the verge of breaking down.

1111
00:46:07,485 --> 00:46:10,226
Man Sik, I'm treating the Chinese buyers today.

1112
00:46:10,226 --> 00:46:11,226
Join me.

1113
00:46:11,226 --> 00:46:14,926
Yeol Chan's revenge never stops.

1114
00:46:17,866 --> 00:46:19,636
Are there no interpreters?

1115
00:46:19,935 --> 00:46:23,235
Yeol Chan canceled them this morning.

1116
00:46:23,706 --> 00:46:25,906
Yeol Chan asked him to join because he doesn't know Chinese.

1117
00:46:25,906 --> 00:46:28,406
He wanted to humiliate him.

1118
00:46:28,605 --> 00:46:29,775
However.

1119
00:46:33,346 --> 00:46:34,846
That man.

1120
00:46:36,855 --> 00:46:39,755
Because of this thick-skinned and clueless intern,

1121
00:46:39,755 --> 00:46:43,355
their contract almost didn't work out, but maybe not.

1122
00:46:45,295 --> 00:46:46,656
Thanks, Man Sik.

1123
00:46:46,965 --> 00:46:50,025
The buyer liked Korea's drinking culture,

1124
00:46:50,025 --> 00:46:51,965
so he signs the contract.

1125
00:46:52,235 --> 00:46:56,266
How did you get pushed over by that oldie?

1126
00:46:56,665 --> 00:46:59,875
It taints his reputation he worked hard to build.

1127
00:47:00,645 --> 00:47:02,775
Is General Manager Ga out of his mind?

1128
00:47:02,775 --> 00:47:04,116
I know.

1129
00:47:04,116 --> 00:47:05,976
- That was terrible. - Terrible?

1130
00:47:05,976 --> 00:47:07,915
He instantly turns from an angel boss...

1131
00:47:07,915 --> 00:47:09,485
into a terrible one.

1132
00:47:09,485 --> 00:47:12,456
Stop acting up.

1133
00:47:12,616 --> 00:47:16,085
Because of Man Sik, his life is messed up now.

1134
00:47:16,085 --> 00:47:19,755
What kind of an idiot sent ramyeon to Yeonggok Borough Office?

1135
00:47:19,996 --> 00:47:21,496
Then one day...

1136
00:47:22,096 --> 00:47:23,226
I did.

1137
00:47:23,395 --> 00:47:24,636
- Is there a problem? - Oh, dear.

1138
00:47:24,636 --> 00:47:26,196
The kkondae intern makes a huge mistake...

1139
00:47:26,196 --> 00:47:29,165
and sends the wrong ramyeon order.

1140
00:47:29,806 --> 00:47:32,906
How can you work when you can't see?

1141
00:47:33,335 --> 00:47:35,706
It's 300 boxes, so our team is not enough.

1142
00:47:35,706 --> 00:47:37,446
Let's go before anything happens.

1143
00:47:37,676 --> 00:47:40,145
He causes trouble to all employees,

1144
00:47:40,145 --> 00:47:42,145
but it ultimately gets taken care of.

1145
00:47:42,145 --> 00:47:43,485
- Great work. - Thank you.

1146
00:47:43,485 --> 00:47:46,185
- Are you crying? - I'm not.

1147
00:47:47,386 --> 00:47:49,726
I feel like I'm a nuisance to the team.

1148
00:47:50,295 --> 00:47:51,596
However...

1149
00:47:51,956 --> 00:47:55,395
You're not a nuisance to the team. You're a stepping stone.

1150
00:47:55,395 --> 00:47:58,266
What does he have in mind now?

1151
00:47:58,266 --> 00:47:59,636
This is it.

1152
00:47:59,636 --> 00:48:02,105
This is the advanced way of harassing him.

1153
00:48:02,105 --> 00:48:05,105
Yeol Chan turns much more immature.

1154
00:48:05,105 --> 00:48:08,346
You called the angel terrible.

1155
00:48:08,346 --> 00:48:10,145
Cancel it now.

1156
00:48:10,145 --> 00:48:11,976
General Manager Ga is not terrible.

1157
00:48:11,976 --> 00:48:14,145
There's somebody else who's actually terrible.

1158
00:48:14,145 --> 00:48:17,215
As he planned, his reputation improves.

1159
00:48:17,215 --> 00:48:19,286
Right as he thought he got his perfect revenge...

1160
00:48:19,286 --> 00:48:21,985
