1161
00:48:21,985 --> 00:48:24,226
Man Sik, are you at the office?

1162
00:48:24,226 --> 00:48:25,226
Yes?

1163
00:48:25,395 --> 00:48:26,895
I'll send you an email,

1164
00:48:26,895 --> 00:48:30,335
