1174
00:48:50,956 --> 00:48:52,685
That's not taking responsibility.

1175
00:48:53,215 --> 00:48:55,085
You're running away.

1176
00:48:55,355 --> 00:48:58,156
The kkondae intern surrenders.

1177
00:48:59,096 --> 00:49:02,065
You're not even half as good as Onggol.

1178
00:49:02,065 --> 00:49:03,665
How dare you act up?

1179
00:49:03,665 --> 00:49:05,895
If you like Onggol that much, get lost.

1180
00:49:05,895 --> 00:49:07,806
I'm going to go, jerk.

1181
00:49:07,806 --> 00:49:10,435
Stop talking and get lost.

1182
00:49:10,676 --> 00:49:11,875
Right now!

1183
00:49:12,335 --> 00:49:14,775
They're at it again.

1184
00:49:14,775 --> 00:49:16,406
